node.text:
I booked a skin analysis appointment with Babor in Düsseldorf to finally take a closer look at what was going on with my skin. I was shocked to find out what is most likely the problem. It was something I had never considered before 😱🙏🏻
.
I asked so many questions while I was there to try and help you guys learn more about some issues you might be having 🥰
.
How can I prevent pigmentation?How many products is too much? What are the basics I need? Learn about all this and much more in this video ❤️ In collaboration with @baborofficial
.
If you have any more questions I am happy to answer below ☺️
Lots of Love
Marie

node.text:
Jake has been trying to learn German for 4 years, how do you think he is going? 😂

I have to give him credit, at least he is trying. The key to learning a new language is to not be afraid to make mistakes and to try even if it’s embarrassing 🙏🏻😅 Jake definitely doesn’t mind being embarrassed which is a start! Do any of you guys have tips or tricks to learn faster? 
As of right now there has never been a better time to start learning some things we’ve always wanted to but have never had the time ☺️ For Jake that is German, for me it is learning to develop our website 🙈 What have you always wanted to learn?
#german #language #couples #stayhome #staysafe #selfimprovement

node.title: Just an Aussie guy trying to learn German 😂

node.text:
Find yourself to find the one ❤️ —>

One of the things I’m most proud of is the 6 months of time I spent finding myself, before I found Jake ❤️

18 months before I met Jake I went through the worst, most painful period of my life! I broke down several times and at times I honestly never thought I would be happy ever again 😢 It took everything I had but 6 months before I met Jake I started on a journey to try and live a life that would make me happy again!

Through all the pain and all the heartbreak I was able to find myself and not long after I found the love of my life 🥰

What I learnt was the importance of working on yourself and finding who you truly are and what you truly want 🙏🏻 When you’ve done that you’re ready for the perfect partner to walk into your life.

And they will, trust me 😌
